OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNew law to protect workers 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffrom sex harassment        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Workers are set to get more protection 
OL,6, from sexual harassment in the workplace
OL,7, after MPs approved a new law.          
OL,9,FThe Worker Protection Bill, introduced 
OL,10,Fby Liberal Democrat MP Wera Hobhouse,  
OL,11,Fputs a duty on bosses to stop          
OL,12,Fharassment instead of relying on       
OL,13,Femployees to report incidents.         
OL,15,FHowever, the bill had been watered down
OL,16,Fafter opposition in the House of Lords 
OL,17,Fover concerns it could expose employers
OL,18,Fto costly lawsuits.                    
OL,20,FOne Tory MP said it had been "gutted". 
